data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful two story home in Braxton Parke HOA community in Amelia, West Clermont Schools. This home features 4BR, 2.5BA, 2422 square feet with unfinished walkout basement with rough in and plenty of storage and situated on a 0.33 acre lot on cul de sac with a private wooded backyard. Hardwood floors and fireplace in living room with open kitchen and oversized mud room off garage. Primary BR with en suite bathroom featuring double sink vanity, walk in shower/bathtub and large walk in closet. New carpet 2019, A/C 2018 with 10 year warranty, deck addition 2020. Fresh paint. Nothing to do but move in!
